          ></path><path
            d="M6 7h6v6H6zm7 8H6v2h12v-2h-4zm1-4h4v2h-4zm0-4h4v2h-4z"></path>
        </svg>
        <span
          class="text-sm font-light uppercase tracking-tight hidden md:block"
        >
          Blog
